title: South Korean Seong-Jin Cho wins Chopin Piano Competition
text:
> Entertainment South Korean Seong-Jin Cho wins Chopin Piano Competition Seong-Jin Cho of South Korea smiles after he was announced the winner of the 17th International Frederic Chopin Piano Competition in Warsaw, Poland, Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015.
